程序包 org.janusgraph.core.attribute

类 TinkerPopTextWrappingPredicate

java.lang.Object
org.janusgraph.core.attribute.TinkerPopTextWrappingPredicate
所有已实现的接口:
BiPredicate<Object,​Object>, JanusGraphPredicate
public class TinkerPopTextWrappingPredicate
extends Object
implements JanusGraphPredicate
A JanusGraphPredicate that just wraps a TinkerPop Text predicate. This enables JanusGraph to use TinkerPop Text predicates in places where it expects a JanusGraphPredicate.
